Join us for the weekend or just for the day as we become Girl Scout Investigators.  Learn how to follow clues and solve mysteries.  Junior and Cadette leaders:  Bring your badge books as the girls will meet some of the requirements for the Detective and Special Agent badges.

** the Saturday only session runs from 8:30am to 6:30pm and includes lunch and supper

** Camporees are open to all Girl Scouts of Gateway Council who are registered for the 2016 Membership year.  All adults must be registered and approved volunteers for the 2016 membership year.

** Adult spots are limited, please follow the adult to girl ratios in Safety Activity Checkpoints.  Note: Daisies must have a one to one ratio.
